    <div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><p>The Re-entry Student Program offers two scholarships: <strong>Crankstart</strong> for newly admitted students, and <strong>Osher</strong> for continuing students.  Applications for these scholarships are open during each Fall term and typically have deadlines around the end of September/early October.</p>

