    <div class="fieldable-panels-pane">
    <div class="field field-name-field-basic-text-text field-type-text-long field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><p><span>The Crankstart Re-entry Scholarship provides up to $5,000 awards to ten first-semester (if you began taking courses during summer, you may still apply) undergraduate re-entry students who demonstrate the potential and capacity to positively contribute to society beyond Berkeley.</span></p></div></div></div></div>
  </div>

  
